    "@type": "Event",
    "name": "Unplug: Brick Your Phone",
    "url": "https://puttingscene.com/events/4671",
    "startDate": "2026-06-14T11:00:00+05:30",
    "endDate": "2026-06-14T13:00:00+05:30",
    "description": "<p>A workshop that teaches how to use NFC stickers to physically block apps on our phone + a discussion around how we can use our phones and social media more mindfully + an invite into a WhatsApp group where participants serve as accountability partners to each other.</p><p>If you've spent more time sending reels to your friends than actually talking to them, this one's for you.</p><p>We\u2019re living in a state of constant digital overwhelm. Unplug is here to change that. \ud83c\udf3f</p><p>By joining this workshop, you\u2019ll learn how to use NFC tools to block your social media apps in a way that <em>actually stops you</em> from scrolling all night long. \ud83d\udcf5</p><p><strong>In this session, you\u2019ll</strong></p><p>- Choose a personalised design for your setup</p><p>- Learn how to use NFC stickers to block apps</p><p>- Reflect on your intentions with social media</p><p>- Meet accountability partners that\u2019ll help you cut down your weekly screen time</p><p>- Find ways to make your phone work for YOU</p><p><strong>\u26a0\ufe0f Please note:</strong></p><p>- No prior tech knowhow required</p><p>- Some older phones may not have NFC compatibility in which case QR codes will be substituted</p><p>There\u2019s too much life to live to keep our heads stuck in our phones. Come unplug with us, and take that first step. \u2601\ufe0f</p><p><strong>What is Unplug?</strong></p><p>Unplug is a series of events designed to help you put down your phones and be more present in your life. Between screen fatigue and social media addiction, it\u2019s easy to feel disconnected. Through hands-on analog workshops, mental reset sessions and a vibrant creative community, Unplug brings you one step closer to a more intentional and present lifestyle.&nbsp;</p>",
